-------------Closed/Hired-------------

Job Title: Fullstack developer 5+ 

Company: Everse 

Salary: around  1000$ 

Description:
 We offers a cutting-edge tax compliance platform that utilizes artificial intelligence and cloud technology. We achieved great success by transforming the VAT/GST recovery process through its cloud-based enterprise recovery solution. With the power of intelligent automation, We assists major corporations, even those in the Fortune 500, in obtaining valuable insights from their transactional data. This empowers finance and tax experts with comprehensive data integrity, strict compliance, and significant cost savings.

Requirements:
5+ years experience of relevant experience as a full-stack developer;
3+ years experience with Angular 2+;
3+ years experience with Node (Express);
Experience with MySQL;
Experience with MongoDB;
Experience with Git;
Agile. Principles and processes;
English level - Intermediate and/or higher (conversational and written), as all the main communication with the team is in English.

Desirable:
Experience with Kubernetes.


Responsibilities:
Develop new features and maintain existing applications;
Implement 3rd party integrations;
Deliver high-quality code;
Effectively collaborate with the team to provide the best solutions;
Stay up-to-date with emerging technologies and trends in development.


Team composition:
5 developers.


Social package: 
Stable long-term project 
Vacation is 20 working days / 4 working days per year for sick leaves 
Annual performance evaluations 
Flexible work schedule 
Communicating directly with the customer
For more details and sending CVs please PM me 

